metadata.name: Pawning the Star
metadata.description:
This fun guy doesn't need a long introduction! He can get the best price on almost anything and negotiate with you to the point where you would be glad to leave the item as a present!

Imaging him running an NFT Pawn shop?! ...Still haven't figured out? His nick name rhymes with NFT!

-----

Unique digitally hand-drawn 1/1 NFT minted exclusively on Foundation.

30% of the profits will go towards the community-selected charity.
